W,A,S,D=draw straight lines
Button 1(not numpad)=Change colour to White
Button 2(not numpad)=Change colour to Blue
Button 3(not numpad)=Change colour to Yellow
Button 4(not numpad)=Change colour to Green
R=Chane colour to Red
Q=clear the screen

//Everything you draw stays untill you clear the screen or shutdown the computer

